  "detailed_description": "Vade Retro is a PvP exorcism game up to 4 players. Play as Demon and make your opponents go through hell, or join the exorcist team by choosing a specialty to save victims from the devil's grip in this action-packed experience. <br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/40519fdf66271cc042124e8f446b4e98.poster.avif?t=1667363073\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/40519fdf66271cc042124e8f446b4e98.webm?t=1667363073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/40519fdf66271cc042124e8f446b4e98.mp4?t=1667363073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your team</h2>Play with your friends or with other players online. You can become the demon or play in co-op if you want to be a member of the exorcist team. By joining it, you will have the choice of 3 roles: the priest, the medic or the engineer.<br><br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/c7c19b0db5061e1db391e3c3496fc925.avif?t=1667363073\" width=616 height=270 /></span><br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/45f39c5cc116bafcc04b1e5c684349d3.poster.avif?t=1667363073\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/45f39c5cc116bafcc04b1e5c684349d3.webm?t=1667363073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/45f39c5cc116bafcc04b1e5c684349d3.mp4?t=1667363073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>The Priest</strong>: Speak incantations and defy the laws of nature by summoning spirits.<br></li><li><strong>The Medic</strong> : Heal your teammates and use your potions to defeat the demon.<br></li><li><strong>The Engineer</strong>: Use your equipment to help your teammates progress through the game.</li></ul><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/aa7147174808aaa0354e6ad0731238e0.poster.avif?t=1667363073\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/aa7147174808aaa0354e6ad0731238e0.webm?t=1667363073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/aa7147174808aaa0354e6ad0731238e0.mp4?t=1667363073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Progression in the game</h2>Take advantage of the different maps, each with its own particularities, in order to unlock spells, potions, or equipment that will help you progress in the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game experience</h2>Live an experience between horror and action thanks to realistic and captivating universes and dynamic gameplay based on the physics engine.",
  "about_the_game": "Vade Retro is a PvP exorcism game up to 4 players. Play as Demon and make your opponents go through hell, or join the exorcist team by choosing a specialty to save victims from the devil's grip in this action-packed experience. <br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/40519fdf66271cc042124e8f446b4e98.poster.avif?t=1667363073\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/40519fdf66271cc042124e8f446b4e98.webm?t=1667363073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/40519fdf66271cc042124e8f446b4e98.mp4?t=1667363073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose your team</h2>Play with your friends or with other players online. You can become the demon or play in co-op if you want to be a member of the exorcist team. By joining it, you will have the choice of 3 roles: the priest, the medic or the engineer.<br><br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/c7c19b0db5061e1db391e3c3496fc925.avif?t=1667363073\" width=616 height=270 /></span><br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/45f39c5cc116bafcc04b1e5c684349d3.poster.avif?t=1667363073\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/45f39c5cc116bafcc04b1e5c684349d3.webm?t=1667363073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/45f39c5cc116bafcc04b1e5c684349d3.mp4?t=1667363073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>The Priest</strong>: Speak incantations and defy the laws of nature by summoning spirits.<br></li><li><strong>The Medic</strong> : Heal your teammates and use your potions to defeat the demon.<br></li><li><strong>The Engineer</strong>: Use your equipment to help your teammates progress through the game.</li></ul><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/aa7147174808aaa0354e6ad0731238e0.poster.avif?t=1667363073\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/aa7147174808aaa0354e6ad0731238e0.webm?t=1667363073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1931950/extras/aa7147174808aaa0354e6ad0731238e0.mp4?t=1667363073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Progression in the game</h2>Take advantage of the different maps, each with its own particularities, in order to unlock spells, potions, or equipment that will help you progress in the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game experience</h2>Live an experience between horror and action thanks to realistic and captivating universes and dynamic gameplay based on the physics engine.",
